==English==
===Etymology===
From Latin ''renuntiare''

===Noun===
'''renounce'''
#''(Cards)'' an act of renouncing ''(see below)''

===Transitive verb===
'''renounce'''
#give up, resign, surrender
#cast off, repudiate
#decline further association with someone or something
#abandon, forsake, discontinue (an action, habit, intention, etc), sometimes by open declaration

===Intransitive verb===
'''renounce'''
#make a [[renunciation]] of something
#surrender formally some right or trust
#''(Cards)'' fail to [[follow suit]]; playing a card of a different suit when having no card of the suit led

